{"tid":1631914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[遍地落區公投] 連登已被嚴重滲透，任何風向公投都唔應該再係連登搞","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T07:55:20.000Z","uid":251119,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4a970d13f1df20ef9e9ce3031015fd4df9b4278e","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"其實大家都明知連登已經嚴重被三毛，風向撚，popo滲透<br />\n點解仲要係連登搞啲風向式既公投？<br />\n<br />\n例如：集中 vs 遍地 / 裝修 vs 唔裝修 / 私了 vs 唔私了<br />\n陣地 vs 快閃/ 等人權法過先升級 vs keep住升級<br />\n勇武退場 vs 晚晚開花<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實呢啲風向式既投票，係連登搞會有好大弊害</span></strong><br />\n相信大家呢兩三日都見識到，<br />\n係連登既風向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一係就係平行時空，</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一係就轉得極快</span></strong>，快得非常可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">弊害例子：</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 容易比「別有用心」既風向撚帶到風向<br />\n2. 太多人盲目跟風，一個鐘既隱藏正負皮係唔夠的<br />\n3. 容易比三毛大軍操控結果<br />\n4. 受眾太細，停留左係連登既同溫層<br />\n5. 冇辦法知道連登以外既人係點諗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方法：</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 配合18區遍地開花既行動<br />\n2. 係開花時向民眾收集意見<br />\n3. 民眾包括：發夢手足、街坊、前線、普通平民（包括藍絲）、各店鋪職員老闆<br />\n4. 整理數據之後再公開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但呢個idea係非常初步，<br />\n有好多bug位需要大家一齊諗下點解決：</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 開花時未必有時間做呢樣野<br />\n2. 由邊個去收集同整理數據？<br />\n3. 由邊個最後去公開數據？同係邊到公開？<br />\n4. 應該問啲咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能大家會覺得呢個方法好天馬行空<br />\n但依家既行動實在已經到左樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一，</span></span></strong><br />\n要突破樽頸位既話，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>行動方向同目標一定要多元化，</strong></span><br />\n同埋我地係爭取民主，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">如果連我地自己都唔民主既話，</span></strong><br />\n我地做既野真係可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">令人信服</span></strong>咩？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二，</span></span></strong><br />\n呢個行動係可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">將抗爭徹底帶入社區</span></strong>，<br />\n將抗爭<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>社區化，平民化，普及化，</strong></span><br />\n如果我地可以令社區既每一個人，<br />\n都有機會可以<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">「參與」係呢場抗爭入面</span></strong>，<br />\n佢地先會覺得<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>係我地既一份子</strong></span>，<br />\n而唔係以「示威者」「暴徒」「個班後生仔」黎<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">標籤</span></strong>我地<br />\n撕破左呢啲標籤，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">先可以令更多既人加入我地</span></strong><br />\n要將平民百姓<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">口中既「佢地 (示威者」變成 「我地」</span></strong><br />\n比佢地覺得佢地都係參與緊我地，<br />\n咁樣先做到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「全民抗爭」</span></strong></span>，<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>呢個行動可以話係「全民抗爭」既上台階。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>第三，</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n要咁樣做，先可以真正知道其他人係點諗我地，<br />\n點諗我地既行動，對我地既行動有咩意見，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你地成日都話要顧及示威者既形象同光環，</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>但你地又唔去問下人點睇你地，</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">問番自己既手足點睇自己有用咩？</span></strong></span><br />\n你要知人地點諗你，最直接就緊係去問人架啦<br />\n係到估下估下有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">依家既行動實在太單一，<br />\n之前香港人既抗爭智慧同創意去哂邊？<br />\n我呢個諗法非常初步，<br />\n好需要大家既意見去改善</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c229ba29f0bf5034571ab80d84cb85b6a560915b","tid":1631914,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"97bb382e97d218357654beb704e135f239e8c1c6","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4ad78a013bbc2a20c6ddbd0f556b62975e56f772","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fee648d7ab454f55847dea51552184cd3df3073e","tid":1631914,"uid":99397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7ded587b3a95b79ba27c5275ddb8eba63df0352b","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"大家比下意見啦<br />\n覺得好定唔好都講下啦"},{"pid":"cfa7cf0220ec8f05d0b4d8d9f536e168104b280b","tid":1631914,"uid":217185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb32edf857e3569d7340a12c7a96c13845627d37","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"baa4f9f61e786741616a5b82174180f405f045b4","tid":1631914,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單<br />\n<br />\n做自己覺得係啱嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我連續兩日都去左港島 <br />\n<br />\n咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行無錯<br />\n<br />\n勇武亦都無錯<br />\n<br />\n只要你覺得啱就無錯"},{"pid":"1742e31e9b204dbf89f11fa073d4a00fb6469061","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"推到有人比下意見"},{"pid":"7ec6b812f580adc3950c46a62a179b3386794f17","tid":1631914,"uid":293667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:38.000Z","msg":"如果香港人權及民主法案通過唔到<br />\n請準備好 港共光明正大殺人啦<br />\n<br />\n［停一停諗一諗］花少少時間睇 你覺得政府係咪真係冇做野？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630572</a><br />\n<br />\n［花10秒睇保護自已］千祈唔好以為啲狗好蠢 其實佢哋不斷做緊嘢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1617712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1617712</a>"},{"pid":"fa2a89de37dfab9143acdbd9385c57140c243287","tid":1631914,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f11f120d2ef10cc5ff0acd9dd32b052c2396a1a9","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa4f9f61e786741616a5b82174180f405f045b4","tid":1631914,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單<br />\n<br />\n做自己覺得係啱嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我連續兩日都去左港島 <br />\n<br />\n咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行無錯<br />\n<br />\n勇武亦都無錯<br />\n<br />\n只要你覺得啱就無錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"但依家就係有一堆分化撚，<br />\n以「自己覺得錯」同「有人覺得你錯」去批鬥其他人<br />\n佢地好中意話：依家好多人xxxxx啦，唔好再xxxx<br />\n然後就會有好撚多人信哂，<br />\n但根本就冇人知係咪真係咁多人覺得個樣野唔岩<br />\n<br />\n做到全民公投既，就可以阻止到連登分化"},{"pid":"0582bb7e9e9b51cbab836df2a7dcc44ef90ce851","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1899e9a64c0d70f6d36c03db5f053d495710e163","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8abfaacdd6409d09262a82b1c9a2a9c01ce08f96","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa19eb07ad426021cbcbc9aea8c2fca2f47f1481","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a509d649382a22aaff8f0813666f74afb8b747c","tid":1631914,"uid":48670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"連登完全失去作用<br />\n啲言論仲惡劣過立場facebook啲留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f670cd831a3d17f9c824e38b82b6fac4ba708d29","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a509d649382a22aaff8f0813666f74afb8b747c","tid":1631914,"uid":48670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"連登完全失去作用<br />\n啲言論仲惡劣過立場facebook啲留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"所以絕對需要另覓一個新既平台既收集「真」既意見。。"},{"pid":"84c2f1a219ecdd8628508a5681ffcd9947730f72","tid":1631914,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3698c3103b99fd1778e6e5e8035382f9b50448f","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"再係咁落係，<br />\n真係成也連登，敗也連登"},{"pid":"d15fc9c89712eae544c79a69537f67d6bffe7b22","tid":1631914,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11f120d2ef10cc5ff0acd9dd32b052c2396a1a9","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa4f9f61e786741616a5b82174180f405f045b4","tid":1631914,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單<br />\n<br />\n做自己覺得係啱嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我連續兩日都去左港島 <br />\n<br />\n咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行無錯<br />\n<br />\n勇武亦都無錯<br />\n<br />\n只要你覺得啱就無錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"但依家就係有一堆分化撚，<br />\n以「自己覺得錯」同「有人覺得你錯」去批鬥其他人<br />\n佢地好中意話：依家好多人xxxxx啦，唔好再xxxx<br />\n然後就會有好撚多人信哂，<br />\n但根本就冇人知係咪真係咁多人覺得個樣野唔岩<br />\n<br />\n做到全民公投既，就可以阻止到連登分化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"可以客觀分析，等手足自己決定，可以幫手諗埋解決方法"},{"pid":"f285d6382a339f80cc5e8c1169d096984b9d5b32","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"我地要將抗爭帶出連登呀。。。<br />\n唔好再縮係連登到<br />\n話人井底之蛙，其實可能連登先至係井底"},{"pid":"f8bb913571a94bc6f6932a9dd68fa16fa9ad9039","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d15fc9c89712eae544c79a69537f67d6bffe7b22","tid":1631914,"uid":86403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11f120d2ef10cc5ff0acd9dd32b052c2396a1a9","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa4f9f61e786741616a5b82174180f405f045b4","tid":1631914,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單<br />\n<br />\n做自己覺得係啱嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我連續兩日都去左港島 <br />\n<br />\n咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n和理非遊行無錯<br />\n<br />\n勇武亦都無錯<br />\n<br />\n只要你覺得啱就無錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"但依家就係有一堆分化撚，<br />\n以「自己覺得錯」同「有人覺得你錯」去批鬥其他人<br />\n佢地好中意話：依家好多人xxxxx啦，唔好再xxxx<br />\n然後就會有好撚多人信哂，<br />\n但根本就冇人知係咪真係咁多人覺得個樣野唔岩<br />\n<br />\n做到全民公投既，就可以阻止到連登分化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"可以客觀分析，等手足自己決定，可以幫手諗埋解決方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"你起我底就知，我由7月到依家<br />\n不斷開post叫人獨立思考<br />\n差唔多每個post都係勸人要有獨立思考<br />\n但到依家十月，大家都係中意比人扯住個鼻走<br />\n就知道連登仔根本好懶得去自己分析<br />\n多數中意聽人講"},{"pid":"ae03b95ade7a5f7b8afe98ab865fc77ce7b1868d","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06c17ebcd688e97fc06c1cf7f617862d514bed53","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7f009d5e7fb1c466a1dde6a21ad8f72b6e689e2e","tid":1631914,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"4c7a52bf1f99962a2179fe1a8b193863b2bc0577","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bed57d9cfcbd04993b265a58785877691d3bc50c","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c3ea643371fb2561443c28337d0ed7ee73b1065","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b5b0d717289ff5427a145f35207880d4a97020cc","tid":1631914,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8076040c9020f2ee7cf7a1a3e4fd653f36ebd40d","tid":1631914,"uid":52609,"